descriptionHtml:
THIER IS A LITTLE VIDEO ON IT IF YOU WANA KNOW WHAT IT LOOKS LIKE BUT IT HAS CHANGED A BIT AND ALL THE BUGS THAT YOU SEE IN THE VIDEO HAVE BEEN FIXED
This is an abondoned tree house.
It contains a bottom story and top story
It is placed high up in the mountains
It comes with everything a good player home comes with
It has a MAPMARKER once you discoverd it
To get thier either look on the pciture to get an idea
where it is or just type COC TREEHOUSE to spawn near it
It as a pretty good view
Im pretty sure you guys will like it
please give me feedback
